/a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p>许多艺术家都在“受折磨的诗人部门”中被点名。主打歌提到了“Lucy”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/who-is-the-lucy-name-checked-on-taylor-swifts-tortured-poets-department-3620144">粉丝们似乎相信这指的是</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>获奖乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">boygenius 的三分之一成员 Lucy Dacus。</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-internet-reacts-to-taylor-swift-name-checking-charlie-puth-on-the-tortured-poets-department-3619909">查理·普斯 (Charlie Puth) 因同一首歌而受到热烈欢迎</a>，而歌迷们也在猜测<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/is-taylor-swifts-thank-you-aimee-about-kim-kardashian-3620097">“thanK you aIMee”是否是针对金·卡戴珊 (Kim Kardashian) 的</a>。</p><p>斯威夫特还在《Guilty As Sin?》中点名了苏格兰独立乐队 The Blue Nile，这似乎是对希利的又一次致敬。</p><p>在<em>NME</em>对斯威夫特新专辑的三星级评论中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">它进一步谈到了希利和斯威夫特在《但爸爸我爱他》中的关系</a>，“这似乎是她对她与 1975 年主唱马蒂·希利短暂关系的强烈反对的回应”。</p><p> “他们转瞬即逝的浪漫似乎是这张专辑大部分内容的缪思，引发了她的粉丝群的爆炸性反应，他们对斯威夫特与这位歌手的公开联系感到心烦意乱，因为他发表了一系列<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/matty-healy-says-podcast-controversy-actually-doesnt-matter-3449380">有争议的评论</a>（其中一些评论很快就围绕着她） -未来的合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-spice">Ice Spice</a> ）。”</p><p>唱片发行后，斯威夫特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-international-dates-for-eras-tour-3458456">将于下个月在欧洲恢复她职业生涯的“Eras Tour”，然后于六月前往英国和爱尔兰</a>。作为竞选的一部分，斯威夫特将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-adds-two-new-london-eras-shows-with-paramore-3538573">今年夏天在伦敦温布利体育场进行八场演出</a>，并得到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">帕拉莫尔</a>的支持。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/patti-smith-responds-to-taylor-swift-name-check-on-the-tortured-poets-department-3703931">帕蒂·史密斯 (Patti Smith) 回应泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在“受折磨的诗人部门”中的名字检查的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 2024 年唱片店日吸引粉丝提前排队抢购限量版唱片https://www.nme.com/news/music/record-store-day-2024-has-fans-queuing-early-to-grab-limited-edition-releases-3702732?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=record- 2024 年商店日有粉丝排队抢先抢购限量版Emma WilkesSat, 20 Apr 2024 12:27:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsRecord Store Day https://www.nme.com/?p=3702732 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年唱片店日" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>独立唱片店的年度庆典吸引了大批歌迷前来抢购限量版唱片</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/record-store-day-2024-has-fans-queuing-early-to-grab-limited-edition-releases-3702732">2024 年唱片店日后，粉丝们早早排队抢购限量版，该版本</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年唱片店日" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今天（4 月 20 日），<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/record-store-day">唱片店日</a>迎来了第 17 届，歌迷们从凌晨起就开始排队，等待从当地独立唱片店购买特别版唱片。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/record-store-day-2024-full-list-releases-vinyl-3588062">2024 年唱片店日：查看完整发行列表</a></strong></li></ul><p>一些大牌乐队为这一年度活动推出了特别的一次性收藏黑胶唱片和磁带，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">David Bowie</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daft-punk">Daft Punk</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/talking-heads">Talking Heads</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/talking-heADS">Paramore</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lily-allen">Lily Allen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gorillaz">Gorillaz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">Elton John</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">Paramore</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">Noel Gallagher 的 High Flying鸟儿</a>。</p><p>金斯顿的宴会唱片公司在他们的社交媒体上表示，唱片店日大使<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">帕拉摩尔</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-byrne">大卫·伯恩</a>的分手是迄今为止最受欢迎的特别版本。其中包括 Paramore <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-paramores-return-with-cover-of-talking-heads-burning-down-the-house-3579806">翻唱的 Talking Heads 的“Burning Down The House”，</a>而 Byrne 翻唱了他们的歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-byrne-to-cover-paramores-hard-times-for-record-store-day-2024-3597053">“Hard Times”。</a> </p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"><img src="htt